What you need to know:

Former Cabinet Minister and ex-Nyaribari Chache MP, Simeon Nyachae, has died at the age of 88. His body is currently at the Lee Funeral Home in Nairobi. In life, Mr Nyachae’s critics thought and openly dismissed him as arrogant and dictatorial – perhaps too pushy.He was a man who easily crossed swords with those who crossed his path and did not suffer fools gladly.